This paper is about neural machine translation (NMT), which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the computer science category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL). The paper also uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and multilingual models, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions using max-pooling, which is a technique commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV).
